create table if not exists VIEW.SL_WORK_ACTIVITY_NEW_TMP_201908080000_746 stored as ORCFile as SELECT 
 	 customer_laber		
	,activity_id		
	,activity_name		
	,activity_city		
	,activity_address		
	,co_organizer_code		
	,co_organizer_name		
	,activity_start_date		
	,activity_end_date		
	,activity_image_url		
	,activity_content		
	,activity_state		
	,upper_limit		
	,activity_url		
	,remark		
	,create_date		
	,update_date		
	,assign_date,
	   TT.CUST_CODE,
	   TT.crm_inst_org_id,
	   TT.open_date,
	   TT.gyyxhsxr,
	   TT.aum_20t_tavg_500000,
	   TT.AUM,
	   TT.debt_1,
	   TT.JGMC1,
	   M.LR_KHRQ,
case when LR_KHRQ>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and LR_KHRQ<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,7,'D') then 1 else 0 end FISL_OPEN_W,
case when LR_KHRQ>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and LR_KHRQ<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,1,'M') then 1 else 0 end FISL_OPEN_M, 
      M.fund_movt_il_fo,
case when fund_movt_il_fo>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and fund_movt_il_fo<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,7,'D') then 1 else 0 end DT_W,
case when fund_movt_il_fo>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and fund_movt_il_fo<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,1,'M') then 1 else 0 end DT_M, 	  
	  M.cd,
case when cd>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and cd<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,7,'D') then 1 else 0 end  CD_W,   
case when cd>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and cd<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,1,'M') then 1 else 0 end  CD_M,     
     M.pab_bind_open_date_fo,                                                                                                                  
case when pab_bind_open_date_fo>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and pab_bind_open_date_fo<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,7,'D') then 1 else 0 end  pab_bind_W,   
case when pab_bind_open_date_fo>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and pab_bind_open_date_fo<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,1,'M') then 1 else 0 end  pab_bind_M,     
     M.five_open_date,
case when five_open_date>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and five_open_date<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,7,'D') then 1 else 0 end  five_open_W,   
case when five_open_date>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and five_open_date<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,1,'M') then 1 else 0 end  five_open_M,     
H.kc_open_date,
case when kc_open_date>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and kc_open_date<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,7,'D') then 1 else 0 end  kc_open_W,   
case when kc_open_date>=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,0,'D') and kc_open_date<=dt_add(cast(activity_start_date as int) ,1,'M') then 1 else 0 end  kc_open_M,  
M.ZZC_DR2,M.ZZC_DR1, M.is_zkh	 
 FROM
     (SELECT  customer_laber		
	,activity_id		
	,activity_name		
	,activity_city		
	,activity_address		
	,co_organizer_code		
	,co_organizer_name		
	,activity_start_date		
	,activity_end_date		
	,activity_image_url		
	,activity_content		
	,activity_state		
	,upper_limit		
	,activity_url		
	,remark		
	,create_date		
	,update_date		
	,assign_date FROM TMP.T_WORK_ACTIVITY_INFO_NEW WHERE dt = 20190808 ) A 
 LEFT JOIN
                       (
                           SELECT          bank_client_no,
                                            cust_code,
                                     	   crm_inst_org_id,
										   JGMC1,
                                     	   cust_type,
                                     	   cust_status,
                                     	   open_date,
                                     	   wealth_channel,
                                     	   non_trade,
                                     	   gyyxhsxr,
                                     	   aum_20t_tavg_500000,
                                     	   AUM,
                                     	   debt_1
                             FROM
                                 (
                                     SELECT
                           				  B.bank_client_no,
                                            B.cust_code,
                                     	   C.crm_inst_org_id,
										   CC.JGMC1,
                                     	   C.cust_type,
                                     	   C.cust_status,
                                     	   D.open_date,
                                     	   D.wealth_channel,
                                     	   DD.non_trade,
                                     	   E.gyyxhsxr,
                                     	   F.aum_20t_tavg_500000,
                                     	   F.AUM,
                                     	   G.debt_1
                                     FROM
                                            (
                                              select  bank_client_no,cust_code 
                                     		 from FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_ONLINE_BOND_OPERATE  
                                     		 where DT=20190808 and (bank_client_no is not null and bank_client_no<>'')
                                     		 )B  
                                      
                                      LEFT JOIN
                                                FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_CUST_BASIC_INFO  C 
                                      ON B.CUST_CODE=C.CUST_CODE  AND C.DT=20190808
									  
									  LEFT JOIN TMP.IMP_YYB_NEW CC 
									  ON C.crm_inst_org_id=CC.JGID AND CC.DT=20190808
                                      
                                      LEFT JOIN
                                                FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_CUST_COMBINE D 
                                      ON B.CUST_CODE=D.CUST_CODE  AND D.DT=20190808
                                      
                                      LEFT JOIN 
                                                FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_CUST_LABEL  DD
                                      ON B.CUST_CODE=DD.CUST_CODE  AND DD.DT=20190808	
                                      
                                      LEFT JOIN
                                                FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_CUST_VALID E 
                                      ON B.CUST_CODE=E.CUST_CODE  AND E.DT=20190808
                                      LEFT JOIN
                                      (
                                      SELECT CUST_CODE,
                                             aum['aum'] AUM,
                                     		aum_ex['aum_20t_tavg_500000'] aum_20t_tavg_500000 
                                      FROM 
                                             FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_ASSET_ALL  
                                      WHERE DT=20190808 
                                      ) F
                                        ON B.CUST_CODE=F.CUST_CODE
                                      
                                      LEFT JOIN
                                      (
                                      select 
                                                        cust_code,
                                                        sum(debt_1) debt_1
                                                        
                                              from
                                                     fact.UDS_F_FISL_ASSET_ACCT
                                              where dt = 20190808
                                      group by cust_code
                                      ) G
                                      ON B.CUST_CODE=G.CUST_CODE  
                                 ) T  
                                   WHERE bank_client_no<>'' AND ( ((((cust_type between 0 and 4)) and ((non_trade is null or non_trade=0) or (non_trade=1)) 
                                   and ((wealth_channel in (1,2))) and ((cust_status=0) or (cust_status not in (0,8,9)))) ) )
                       ) TT
ON A.customer_laber=TT.bank_client_no
left join 
         (
         select 
                    distinct 
                    a.CUACCT_CODE,                                         five_open_date,
                    case when a.pab_bind_open_date_fo>= a.pab_bind_open_date_fo then pab_bind_open_date_fo end pab_bind_open_date_fo,                                         a.cd,
                    a.fund_movt_il_fo,                    a.LR_KHRQ,                     a.ZZC_DR2,                    a.ZZC_DR1,                     is_zkh         from tmp.TMP_KHSL_SIGNIN_LIST2 a 
          where a.dt = 20190808
          ) M
ON TT.CUST_CODE=M.CUACCT_CODE
LEFT JOIN 
tmp.FISL_KCB_DETAIL  H 
ON TT.CUST_CODE=H.CUST_CODE AND H.DT=20190808
